  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td colspan="2">
    <!--<a href="magic.asp?mode=updateform&amp;ID=391">-->
    <a href="../UserUpdate.asp?ID=391">
    <small><font face="Verdana"><strong>Add New Info Here</strong></font></small>
    </a>
    </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td valign="top" align="left">
		<font face="verdana" size="2">
		<b>Description:</b> <br>
		This spell will Summon a level 11-13 pet. At this point your pet can hit magic mobs or undead that are invulnerable to normal weapons. It does however require a componet.<BR>
<BR>
<B>Location:</B><BR>General
		</font>
	 </td>
	 <td rowspan="4" valign="top" align="right">
    
