			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Ack! Forgot to tell ya what &quot;rev-kite&quot; means... for those not attuned to the concept.<BR>
<BR>
Rev-kite: ie Reverse Kiting<BR>
<BR>
1. Darkness DOT<BR>
2. Sick fuschia with turqoise dots pet on em<BR>
3. Stack DOTs<BR>
4. Fear<BR>
5. Med and wait for fear to wear off<BR>
6. Rinse, repeat 4 thru 5 until good and dead<BR>
7. Poke dead mob to be sure it's dead<BR>
8. Loot, med and move on to the next<BR>
<BR>
Course if you're one of them thar cooperative types... the destructions change. But, I won't be learning that until I can get outta my twenties.(When reputation means EVERYTHING!!!)<BR>
<BR>
8)<BR>
<BR>
Necris
				</font>
