				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				If you're rev-kiting like you are supposed to be... it can be a purple pet with bright orange polka-dots and still be effective!!! Magical hits are with any weapon... as posted earlier. Rusty halberd is still my favorite &quot;non-trophy&quot; weapon to hand my pets.<BR>
<BR>
20dmg per swing on a rev-kite sure speeds things up! Stack that with some darkness and assorted DOTs and it goes even quicker without having to chase the lil' buger all over Norrath to finish him off. Med whilst you wait... leads to faster solo levelling in the long run.<BR>
<BR>
Innoruk be with you, my brethren...<BR>
<BR>
Necris
